        "id": 1068239
      },
      "writtenOn": "2015-03-05T07:44:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think so, because socket_network_client rely on socket_in_client which rely on socket_connect_client. By putting BEGIN/END_NOSIGALRM into it, it prevents connect being interrupted in other parts of the app.\nHaving them in the function also keep the blocking \"smaller\".",
      "parentUuid": "37366cdf_f2e048c4",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 364,
        "startChar": 4,
        "endLine": 364,
        "endChar": 65
      },
      "revId": "e63bf95afe5b5e619700d408cc59a0953f15591d",
